wiki.text:
'Weinstock' () is the name of:
* Arnold Weinstock (1924–2002), English businessman
* Bob Weinstock (1928–2006), founder of Prestige Records
* Marcus Weinstock (born 1984), Swedish professional ice hockey player
* Sophia Petrillo, fictional character in TV series The Golden Girls and its
  spinoffs (full name: Sophia Angelo Spirelli Petrillo Weinstock)
